title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Top 5 busiest airports - Sweden
description:
In this video we will look at the top 5 busiest airports in Sweden. This top 5 contains 3 airports which have been updated by the community. The other two have been updated as part of the World Update which concentrated on the Nordics.

If you want to try the addons yourself download them via the links below:

Goteborg Landvetter Airport(ESGG):
https://flightsim.to/file/27618/esgg-gteborg-landvetter-airport

Stockholm Skavsta Airport )ESKN)
https://flightsim.to/file/6247/eskn-stockholm-skavsta

Stockholm Bromma Airport (ESSB)
https://flightsim.to/file/6313/essb-stockholm-bromma
